HAZYVIEW – Ulusaba Private Game Reserve, a member of Vir gin Limited Edition’s award-winning collection of retreats, is Branson’s safari lodge located in the western sector of the Sabi Sand Private Game Reserve.  “The managers at the lodge heard about us and contacted us to train him while he was visiting Ulusaba. I was blown away by this great opportunity. He is a great and funny guy and he is quite fit for his age,” laughed Taylor. Owner of Core 360, Chaz Taylor trained Sir Richard Branson. 